snippet.title: Need for Speed Rivals - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Put the ultimate rivalry into high stakes action as a Cop or Racer in our innovative new AllDrive system which destroys the line between singleplayer and multiplayer gameplay. Learn More: http://bit.ly/1g97kms

Need for Speed Rivals is available now for PS4 and for pre-order on Xbox One, Xbox 360, PS3 & PC.

Like us on Facebook: http://on.fb.me/11p7cDS
Subscribe to YouTube channel: http://bit.ly/11JVNgW
Follow on Twitter: http://bit.ly/13LgzQD
View photos on Instagram: http://bit.ly/126yvYR

Will You Cross the Line?
